OL,3,C'Marathon man' Gary McKee's final push
OL,4,Cto raise #1m for local hospice
OL,6,FA veteran fundraiser is nearing the
OL,7,Fend of his challenge to run 100
OL,8,Fmarathons in 100 days in a bid to
OL,9,Fraise a further #100,000 for a local
OL,10,Fhospice, making the fundraised total
OL,11,F#1m.
OL,13,F'Marathon man', Gary McKee, from
OL,14,FCleator Moor, Cumbria, has been
OL,15,Frunning 26.2 miles every day since 17
OL,16,FJanuary. The challenge will end on
OL,17,FSunday (April 26) at the London
OL,18,FMarathon.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
