OL,3,C'Marathon man' Gary McKee's final push
OL,4,Cto raise #1m for local hospice
OL,6,FHe is no stranger to a running
OL,7,Fchallenge, having embarked on his
OL,8,Ffirst fundraiser in 2017 after his
OL,9,Ffather was diagnosed with cancer. In
OL,10,F2022 he ran a marathon every day for
OL,11,F365 days.
OL,13,FThe money raised will go toward
OL,14,FHospice at Home West Cumbria. Gary has
OL,15,Fbeen fundraising for the local hospice
OL,16,Ffor years, and hopes to raise a
OL,17,Ffurther #100,000 in a bid to reach an
OL,18,Foverall #1m.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
