FL,353,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777129865
OL,3,C'Marathon man' Gary McKee's final push
OL,4,Cto raise #1m for local hospice
OL,6,FHe said: "The support off people in
OL,7,FWest Cumbria has been amazing. People
OL,8,Fhave been out running every day,
OL,9,Fpeople have been out on their bikes.
OL,11,F"At the halfway point there's people
OL,12,Fwith a cup of tea, and a dry robe if
OL,13,Fit has been raining.
OL,15,F"People have supported even on the
OL,16,Fcycle path, saying hello, even that
OL,17,Fcan make a big difference."
OL,19,FHe will be joined at the London
OL,20,FMarathon by his son, Beau, whose been
OL,21,Frunning some miles with him every day.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
