SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F352A1777129865
OL,3,C'Marathon man' Gary McKee's final push
OL,4,Cto raise #1m for local hospice
OL,6,FIt will mark Gary's 100th and final
OL,7,Frun of the challenge and Beau's first
OL,8,Ftime running the London marathon.
OL,10,FHe will be one of the youngest
OL,11,Fparticipants and is defying the odds
OL,12,Fafter recently being diagnosed with a
OL,13,Fheart condition.
OL,15,FBeau said: "It was obviously a bit
OL,16,Ffrustrating at the start, because I
OL,17,Fwas doing what I would normally do and
OL,18,Fit was way harder to do it.
OL,20,F"But just push through and keep going
OL,21,Fand I'll get it done.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
